**	Note:  System procedures must also be defined in "iaom!iamsystm.c".
**
** History:
**	07/89 (jhw) -- Written.
**	03/13/91 (emerson)
**		Added commandlineparameters (for Topaz release).
**	17-jun-93 (essi)
